  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a medium bowl, whisk together olive oil, smoked paprika, garlic, ginger, chili flakes, fish sauce, brown sugar, and coconut milk.",
    "3. Add the shrimp to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "4. Thread the shrimp onto the skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "5. Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until the shrimp are pink and cooked through.",
    "6. Remove the skewers from the grill and serve hot with steamed rice or noodles."
